Web Designer & UX/UI Designer

Summary:
Highly motivated and detail-oriented web and UX/UI designer with experience in website redesign, UX/UI design, and user research. Proficient in wireframing, visual design, and responsive design. Seeking to contribute to projects that have significance and impact people's lives, and collaborate with professionals to grow and learn new things.

Experience:
Web Designer & UX/UI Designer
- Redesigned the Children's Music School website, creating a new landing page that is visually appealing and easy to navigate
- Conducted thorough analysis of existing websites to identify strengths and weaknesses
- Created detailed wireframes and user flows to ensure intuitive and user-friendly interfaces
- Designed user-friendly interfaces for Pet-Saver-Hub, a web service project for rescuing lost and found animals
- Incorporated interactive elements, such as map features, to enhance user experience
- Utilized responsive design principles to ensure compatibility across all devices

Skills:
- Wireframing
- Visual design
- User research
- Responsive design
- UX/UI design

Career Goals:
- Develop skills in UI/UX design and contribute to projects with significance and impact
- Collaborate with professionals to grow and learn new things

- Prioritize communication, teamwork, and user feedback to ensure effective work and high-quality results

Professional Values:
- Attention to detail and creativity in the design process
- Active interaction with users to collect feedback and improve user experience
- Commitment to putting in maximum effort to ensure high-quality work
- Valuing communication and teamwork to achieve results
